<dialog id="summary-modal" class="summary-modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <button class="close-button" onclick="document.getElementById('summary-modal').close()">×</button>
        <h2>Family Trip Summary – For Your Notes</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Trip:</strong> Japan Countryside Family Bike Adventure</li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> Northern Nagano, Japan (2 hrs from Tokyo, 1 hr from Kanazawa)</li>
            <li><strong>Recommended Duration:</strong> 4–7 days</li>
            <li><strong>Best Season:</strong> April to November</li>
            <li><strong>Estimated Cost:</strong> ¥150,000–¥190,000 / person (based on group size)</li>
            <li><strong>Includes:</strong> Lodging, meals, bike rental, support vehicle, guide, cultural activities</li>
            <li><strong>Private & Custom:</strong> Planned around your family’s pace, interests, and the season</li>
            <li>
                <strong>Website:</strong>
                <a href="/explore/family-bike-rural-nagano/" target="_blank"
                    >onelifejapan.com/explore/family-bike-rural-nagano/</a
                >
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>This is not a packaged tour — every trip is planned one-on-one, based on what excites you most.</p>
    </div>
</dialog>

<a href="#" onclick="document.getElementById('summary-modal').showModal(); return false;" class="summary-link">
    Summary for Your Notes
</a>

<style>
    .summary-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--bs-link-color);
        text-decoration: underline;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .summary-modal::backdrop {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }
    .summary-modal {
        max-width: 90%;
        width: 500px;
        margin: auto;
        border: none;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: white;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        text-align: left;
    }
    .summary-modal .modal-content {
        position: relative;
    }
    .summary-modal h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .summary-modal ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
        list-style: disc;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .summary-modal .close-button {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.5rem;
        right: 0.75rem;
        border: none;
        background: none;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
</style>
